name: Contemplation
description:
Standing high on the skybridge, I can
feel how this metropolis becomes so
vividly alive in the night. The delicious
smell from the food stand, the
laughter of lovers and the distant
traffic sound all make me enjoy this
beautiful neon night. Through the
flying jelly fishes, I can feel her looking
at me. I can't take my eyes away from
her dreamy gaze, as if it is telling me
softly her story buried in the past. I
can almost hear her whispering
through the gentle breeze, what a
beautiful encounter on a tranquil night
like this.
